721260f-a.title: Manhattan: Madison Avenue - 32nd Street (East)
721260f-a.text:
Madison Aveme, north from E. 52nd Street (intersection at left) showing a Manhattan arterial canyon formed by loft buildings of the easterly Fifth Avenue district. In the middistance aprears a campaign banner drawn across the thoroughfare from the National Democratic Headquarters at 37th Street. Beyond same and barely outlined is the 40 story structure,
No. 444 Madison Avenue at 49th - 50th Streets.
Fall 1938.
Gift of Fiss Maria V. Leavitt photo
